		<th>Details</th>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td>
		This module provides the Wake-Up features for each room.<br>
		You may select only one hour for one day or select a range of the days to be waking up every day at the same hour.<br>
		Also you may delete one or a range of the days for the one or a group of the rooms.<br>
		<br>
		You may apply a wake-up time for a group.<br>
		This group will be the same like the room selected at first.<br>
		<br>
		</td>
    </tr>
